[normal]5[bold].0[bold]              [bold]Successes to Date[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]5.1
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]In Area 
[normal]B
[normal] (
[normal]Whittle
[normal]s
[normal]ford
[normal] to 
[normal]Cambridge
[normal] city corridor) there is a brand new bus service in place that has been designed by the working group and funded by the County Council. It has been in operation since March 2013 and is 
[normal]very successful. It links a number of villages to key public services (
[normal]such as the health centre in 
[normal]Sawston
[normal]) and also provides a 
[normal]link
[normal] to the 
[normal]Babraham
[normal] 
[normal]Road
[normal] 
[normal]Park
[normal] and Ride site for journeys onwards to 
[normal]Cambridge
[normal]. There is also an interchange opportunity at 
[normal]Sawston
[normal] to the Stagecoach service into 
[normal]Cambridge
[normal]. 
